                            <comment id="16103569" author="cpoerschke" created="Thu, 27 Jul 2017 17:40:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching naive patch to illustrate and semi-fix. Not yet fully tried but I think this will fix the plain &lt;tt&gt;bin/solr stop&lt;/tt&gt; scenario but would break &lt;tt&gt;bin/solr stop -all&lt;/tt&gt; and perhaps also &lt;tt&gt;bin/solr stop -p ...&apos;&lt;/tt&gt; usage.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Separately it might be nice to factor the &apos;SOLR_PORT minus 1000&apos; logic into a little function (it&apos;s currently repeated in at least two places).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16105243" author="cpoerschke" created="Fri, 28 Jul 2017 16:25:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching alternative outline (i.e. broken) patch, the &lt;tt&gt;java_system_property_by_pid&lt;/tt&gt; factor out seems to be not quite right as yet.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
